title: 'Good box
rating: but for lite home setting only'
body: '4.0 out of 5 stars'
column5: Very good toolbox organizer. Have had this since Oct-2022. For keeping tools organized at home for normal repairs and DIY tasks, this box will serve the purpose well. The plastic built quality is just OK, and locking latch is not that sturdy. If you are a professional who carries their toolbox along, do not count on this being sturdy. I don't think this box will endure heavy tools carried inside alongside rough everyday treatment. For that look elsewhere.
